                     <interp inst="t18310630-117-person897" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was a customer of the prosecutors'. I owed them in September last 7l. 3s.; I paid it to the prisoner, and he wrote this receipt, in my presence.</p>
               <p>GEORGE WILSON. I am a customer of the prosecutors'. I owed them some money on the 5th of October; it was 8l. - I gave the money to Bevington, my shopman, who brought me this receipt - there was a discount of 4s.</p>
               <p>- BEVINGTON. I paid this money to the prisoner, and he gave me this receipt.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-117-person898">
                  GEORGE 
                  MARTIN
               <interp inst="t18310630-117-person898" type="surname" value="MARTIN"></interp>
