                     <interp inst="t18310630-117-person898" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the employ of Mr. Ballhe was a customer of the prosecutors'; I paid the prisoner 9l. 0s. 6d. for them - he gave me this receipt.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. My prosecutors told me if I would sign a bill of sale, they would not prosecute me, and they requested me to go to Mr. Abbot for that purpose; he objected to a bill of sale, and proposed a warrant of attorney.</p>
               <p>
